rly in the arrangements of social control. How might these look? Thilo Hagendorff responds to this. His study suggests steps by which to modernize the methodological apparatus of social criticism and increase efficiency for critical social discourses.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aSocial sciencesxPhilosophy. 4aGesellschaft. 4aSozialkritik. 4aSozialphilosophie. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aSteuerung. 4aSystemtheorie. 4aTheorie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology.  aSystems Theory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2014z9783110370416oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014z9783111025223oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383762660540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839426609?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839426609423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839426609/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DSWb2014  aZDB-23-TGPb2014  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016